Do not look for healing at the feet of those who broke you.

Rebuild. 

I got me.

Once you start learning 
The Ls becomes silent

My life got flipped turned upside down

Thank you all for the birthday wishes 

This year was a year lol. Sometimes it takes big life changes to wake you up.

And I’m grateful for all the friends and family who waited patiently until i woke up from awful times and then picked me back up. It’s cheesy but truly, I couldn’t ask for better people to be surrounded by.

Life is too precious to not protect my peace or to live according to other people’s “perfect” ideals and expectations. 

I’ve made a lot of promises to myself over the years on my birthday and I intend to make good on them.

I ain’t nobody can stop me but me.

✌🏾

Fatherhood is amazing. It is also absolutely terrifying. Terrifying to watch you grow. Hopefully never to outgrow me (although outgrow me by height is coming sooner than later) but surpass me in your own way. 

I wouldnt be who I am without you, my son and seeing you step into the world with such confidence, (sometimes maybe overconfidence that I have no idea where it comes from lol) is the greatest lesson and blessing I’ll ever get in life. 

Happy Birthday Tiger, 

- Dad
